summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; authorizing an Easement Agreement to the City of Tukwila for Flood Protection Levee purposes across a portion of the City of Seattle's Cedar River Pipe Line No. 4 Right-of-Way, (CRPL \#4 R/W) aka Bow Lake Pipe Line, adjacent to the Green River located in Government Lot 1, Section 25, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W.M., King County, Washington.
